metadata.name: Embraced by the Mimosa
metadata.description:
Embraced by flowers that bring happiness
Warm spring weather
Fluffy, wrapped up

Read a book of cat's dream stories
Turn the pages slowly
fluffy, bubbly, and warm
Happy time like a dream
___

幸せを呼ぶ花に抱かれて
ぽかぽか 春の陽気
ふわふわ 包まれて

猫の夢のお話
めくるページはゆっくりと
ふわふわ ぽかぽか
ゆめごこち
